<title>HTML TEXT FORMATTING</title></head>
<body>
<h1>Lorem Ipsum</h1>
<p>"<b>Neque</b> porro <strong>quisquam</strong> est <i>qui</i>qui dolorem <em>ipsum</em> quia <mark>dolor</mark> sit amet, consectetur, adipisci velit..."
"There is no one who love<sub>s</sub> <small>pain</small> itself, <big>who</big> seeks after it and wants to have it, <big>simply</big> because it is pain..."</p>
<p><mark>กรวิกศ์ อุ่มเครือ เลขที่12 ม.6/9</mark>
